correctness.rationale: Several core fields are correct (thermal ALD of Al2O3 and ZnO with TMA/H2O and DEZ/H2O, viscous-flow reactor, UHP N2 carrier/purge, 100 °C deposition, 870 cycles, GPCs of 1.1 Å (Al2O3) and 1.9 Å (ZnO), and AFM roughness ~0.27 nm). However, many values are fabricated, inconsistent, or violate the schema: 1) processParameters.plasmaPower is set to null, which violates the schema (should be omitted if not PEALD). 2) processParameters.pressure (100 mTorr) is not reported in the article. 3) processParameters.nucleationPeriod (10 cycles), dosingTime (1000 ms values), purgeTime (1000 ms values), and flowRates (10/100 sccm) are not provided by the article and appear guessed. 4) supercycleDesign (2 Al2O3 : 1 ZnO, i.e., 33% DEZ) conflicts with materialProperties.filmComposition.atomicRatio ('Al:Zn = 1.0:0.2', implying ~20% Zn consistent with 67% DEZ exposures) and with elementalConcentration.values (50%), which is incorrect; article reports ~11% Zn for 50% DEZ and ~20% for 67% DEZ at 100 °C. 5) materialProperties.opticalProperties (refractive index, absorption, band gap, UV-Vis) are not reported in the article. 6) electricalProperties (resistivity value, carrier density, mobility, Hall method) are not measured in this work; resistivity values cited in the paper come from literature (Ω·cm), not Hall data here; unit conversion and composition applicability are unclear. 7) materialProperties.crystallinity: claiming amorphous by XRD is ungrounded (no XRD reported; alloy may be amorphous but not measured here). 8) materialProperties.filmDensity uses 3.0 with unit g/dm3 (schema unit), which numerically conflicts with the article’s 2.7–3.0 g/cm3; if using g/dm3, the numeric should be ~3000 to match 3.0 g/cm3. 9) uniformity (5%) and conformality aspect ratio (10) are not reported. 10) deviceProperties (TFT metrics: μFE, VTH, SS, on/off, deviceStructure) are unrelated to this rf MEMS study and not present in the article. To improve: remove/omit or clearly ground unreported fields, fix schema violation (plasmaPower null), align supercycleDesign with composition and AES values (e.g., use ~20% Zn for 67% DEZ or ~11% for 50% DEZ), correct density units/numbers, and restrict device-level metrics to what is actually reported (rf insertion loss/isolation if schema allowed).

completeness.rationale: Largely incomplete and weakly grounded. (1) Multiple processes in the article are not represented: coatings on released rf MEMS at 100 °C for 0/33/50/67% DEZ (870 cycles, ~100 nm), property films on Si(100) at 100 and 177 °C (600 cycles, 59–68 nm and 69–76 nm), AES films (~25 nm at 100 °C for 0/50/67/100% DEZ), and nanoindentation films (~300 nm at 100 and 177 °C for 0/50/100% DEZ). Only a single process (one alloy/supercycle) is provided. (2) Many values are fabricated or not traceable to the text: reactor pressure (100 mTorr), dosing/purge times (1000 ms), flow rates (10 sccm), nucleation period (10 cycles), uniformity (5%), conformality aspect ratio (10), optical properties (n, absorption, band gap), electrical properties (resistivity, carrier density, mobility), film density (3.0 g/cm3 for 100 °C alloy), and deviceProperties (TFT metrics) that are irrelevant to rf MEMS and not reported. (3) Several reported values conflict with the article: filmComposition lists 50% elemental concentration and atomic ratio 1.0:0.2, whereas AES shows ~11% Zn for 50% DEZ and ~20% Zn for 67% DEZ at 100 °C; device-level metrics reported in the paper (insertion loss ~0.35 dB, isolation ~55 dB at 14 GHz, lifetimes in Table 5) are omitted. (4) Schema issues: plasmaPower is set to null (type violation; should be omitted for TALD), and required sections are populated with ungrounded numbers instead of article-backed values. (5) Partial positives: correct precursors/co-reactant (TMA/H2O; DEZ/H2O), N2 purge, viscous flow reactor, GPCs at 100 °C (Al2O3 1.1 Å/cycle; ZnO 1.9 Å/cycle), 870 cycles and ~100 nm film, roughness ~0.27 nm, and that alloys were formed by substituting DEZ exposures. To improve, add separate process entries for each composition and temperature set reported; include only article-backed parameters (cycle times: 28 s at 100 °C and 12 s at 177 °C; GPCs; cycles; thickness ranges); add dielectric constants (Table 2) with proper units; add AES Zn concentrations; add roughness per Table 1; specify crystallinity per composition/temperature; include rf switch performance (insertion loss, isolation, lifetime) in an appropriate field; remove or justify unreported pressure/flow/dose times; fix units (e.g., resistivity from Ω·cm to Ω·m if included); and remove inapplicable TFT deviceProperties.
